</emphasis>
(Cockerell &amp; Robinson)
</taxonomicName>
; original illustration of the holotype of 
<taxonomicName box="[1140,1255,1916,1937]" class="Insecta" family="Diaspididae" genus="Fiorinia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="297" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coronata">
